Primary_Attributes.Description_Verified: The Kitchen. Aid 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes offers a groundbreaking smart experience and new levels of precision. Features include Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking, a temperature probe for internal temperature updates, and a variety of cooking modes to explore new recipes with confidence. The sleek stainless steel finish and Print. Shield™ resist fingerprints, ensuring your oven looks as good as it cooks.
Primary_Attributes.Product_Title_Verified: KitchenAid 30" Smart Electric Single Wall Oven with Assisted Cooking Modes - Printshield™ Finish
Primary_Attributes.Details_Verified: This advanced KitchenAid wall oven brings smart technology and culinary precision into your kitchen. Its Even-Heat™ True Convection system ensures consistent heat distribution, while the temperature probe and assisted cooking modes make it easier to cook complex dishes. The PrintShield™ finish keeps the oven looking pristine.
Primary_Attributes.Features_List_HTML:
• Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent baking
  • Temperature probe for precise cooking
  • Assisted cooking modes for culinary exploration
  • PrintShield™ finish resists fingerprints
  • Smart appliance capabilities with WiFi connectivity
  • Self-cleaning and steam clean options
  • Air Fry mode for healthier cooking
  • Large capacity for big meals
  • Easy-to-use knob and touch controls
  • UL certified with a 1-year manufacturer warranty

description.final_value: Discover new culinary adventures with KitchenAid's 30-inch Smart Electric Single Wall Oven. Equipped with Even-Heat™ True Convection for consistent results, Assisted Cooking Modes for built-in recipe guidance, and a sleek PrintShield™ Finish. Features include a temperature probe, air fry mode, steam cooking, and Sabbath Mode. Control your oven through the KitchenAid™ App or with voice commands for a seamless cooking experience.

details.final_value: This KitchenAid wall oven brings modern convenience and precision to your kitchen with features like Even-Heat™ True Convection, air fry, steam cooking, and smart controls.
